1. Binance AggTrades to 1-Minute OHLCV Converter
Description

This project converts raw Binance AggTrades historical data into complete 1-minute OHLCV candles enriched with additional market statistics.

The application automatically processes multiple AggTrades CSV files, merges them into a unified dataset, and generates high-quality market data suitable for quantitative analysis, algorithmic trading, backtesting, and machine learning.

Features
Automatic detection of all AggTrades CSV files.
Processing of large historical datasets.
Generation of 1-minute OHLC candles.
Total traded volume calculation.
Buy volume calculation.
Sell volume calculation.
Delta Volume (Buy Volume − Sell Volume).
Number of trades per minute.
Automatic merging of multiple datasets.
Chronological sorting of all candles.
CSV export.
Output Data

Each generated candle contains:

Timestamp
Open
High
Low
Close
Total Volume
Buy Volume
Sell Volume
Delta Volume
Number of Trades
